a vrati 44.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fiboEvenSum(34), 44);"},{"text":"<p><code>fiboEvenSum(60)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 44.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fiboEvenSum(60), 44);"},{"text":"<p><code>fiboEvenSum(1000)</code> treba vratiti 798.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fiboEvenSum(1000), 798);"},{"text":"<p><code>fiboEvenSum(100000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 60696.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fiboEvenSum(100000), 60696);"},{"text":"<p><code>fiboEvenSum(4000000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 4613732.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fiboEvenSum(4000000), 4613732);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-2-even-fibonacci-numbers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-3-largest-prime-factor","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-1-multiples-of-3-or-5","id":"5900f36e1000cf542c50fe81","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-2-even-fibonacci-numbers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}